message.body: Hi! I have to leave for work around 4 but I've got nothing to do before that. What's up?
Hey, sorry. I was busy. I'm in town for a bit and wanted to see if you were free, but I'll just getting free and you're going to work. :[
Aw poo. Well are you leaving today?
Yeah. When are you off work? Late?
Yeah, the problem with baseball is that it doesn't have a set end time. Usually I'm done around 10:30 or so.
I'm afraid I can't stay that long. We'll have to meet next time! I wanted to ask you to keep November 1st free. I'll be in town and wanted to have dinner with everyone.
Okay cool, I'll mark my calendar, lol.
